  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 10,
    "docid": "s_1625_438_0",
    "text": "Yeah, I have andenhonia too, when I can get a task like that done, which takes about an hour cuz ugh, scum, it does give my mind some focus but easy enough to not overwhelm.",
