    "bdi_name": "Concentration Difficulty",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 0,
    "type": "disagreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 10,
    "docid": "s_188_810_30",
    "text": "I had more on our pattern recognition and the value you see when knowing that every object is somewhat real, that there is no fluff, but I can't concentrate at work right now.",
    "bdi_query": 19,
    "bdi_name": "Concentration Difficulty",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 0,
    "type": "disagreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 10,
    "docid": "s_1922_191_7",
    "text": "What helps me cope the best is constantly being distracted, not letting my mind wander.",
    "bdi_query": 19,
    "bdi_name": "Concentration Difficulty",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 0,
    "type": "disagreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 10,
    "docid": "s_1951_200_1",
    "text": "Intellectualising / focusing too much on thoughts (or completely actually, I have not been in touch with my feelings properly, my whole life tbh) is my current hurdle.",
